Installation
Connect to your Raspberry Pi via SSH
Clone this repo: git clone https://github.com/vader7071/rasberry_pi_screenwake.git
Run the setup script: ./rasberry_pi_screenwake/script/install

Uninstallation
If you need to uninstall the power button script in order to use GPIO14 for another project or something:

Run the uninstall script: ./rasberry_pi_screenwake/script/uninstall
